item.title: This Classic Song Will Make You Want to Roll It On Home!
item.description: Introduction Do you ever find yourself humming along to a classic song that you just can’t get out of your head? That’s how we feel about the song “Roll It On Home” by Eddie Rabbitt This classic country song has been around for decades and is still beloved by many Background of the Song “Roll It On Home” was released in 180 as the third single from Eddie Rabbitt’s album Horizon.
